    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, we just got word about that little leak with the 50 user emails. the S3 bucket thing. we need to prep a statement for the press ASAP. how should we frame this so we don't tank our user trust scores? do we call it a breach or find a better way to explain it?",
